SNBC\u2019s 321k) and a +130% lead in the demo 25-54 (122k vs. 53k). CNN ranked #1 this quarter in weekend prime in the key adult 25-54 demo. MSNBC hit its 3rd lowest quarterly P25-54 levels in Total Day in over 10 years, in M-Su Prime in over nine years, and in Daytime 9a-4p in over 15 years. And CNN\u2019s morning program, New Day beat MSNBC\u2019s Morning Joe for the fifth straight quarter among adults 25-54. FULL POST
