aVHavana, Cuba (CNN) Safari trophies, Hollywood stars, covert missions during WWII -- all of them are part of the 21 years that Ernest Hemingway spent at his beloved Cuban home. To celebrate what would be the author's 118th birthday, CNNVR takes you on an exclusive tour of the estate, preserved as he left it 57 years ago.
